MORE Matt is in studio to close out the first work week in November with comedian Mike Baldwin ( https://linktr.ee/Comedianmike ) joining in for the first half. We are going to chew the fat a bit, read some outrageous news stories together, and then end the show with a mix of calls and random media. (Please excuse the 5-7 minutes or so of crackling audio that happening at the end of the guest spot and into the intermission - I got it sorted right after that!) Alllright, let's set a nice tone for the weekend!
